{
  "stem": "19518.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 401.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we had to wait our turn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Meanwhile, night came on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the flame, not from the chimney, but the flame nearby-- later on I realized what it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were over-- working overtime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The ovens could not burn that many bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So some of the bodies were burnt in the pit nearby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that flame from that pit made the night-- I can't say daytime-- I never saw light like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But illuminated the whole area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We did not need the reflecting lights that the guards were throwing at us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They could very well see that we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then the time came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we had to go in single file into that room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we were shaved, every part of our bodies was shaved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we were led into showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were given a piece of soap with RIF on it, Reichs Judan Fett, which means pure Jewish fat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it was a soft piece, a square little soft piece.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I says, which part of my parents or my sisters am I going to be washed with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "That's what went through my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we got in there, and a little water dripped down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Nobody recognized anybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We didn't know who was where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But I recognized a cousin of mine, because she had a little growth near her right ear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went over quiet, and I says [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And here she recognized my name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we stood, supposedly under the shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we waited, and a few drops of water came down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we hear a German announce, a woman announcement, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "That means, soap yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to my cousin, I says, tell me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Does the gas work better when your body is wet?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
